<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">newbie ques about naggy</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">i'm a newbie cleric (this is essentially my first character) just had some questions ... i never bothered with resist gear because 1) im poor 2) im lazy 3) i wouldn't know what to look for anyway. have only been part of 4 attempts on naggy's life, so, i'm probably just ignorant. however i noticed if you were pulling him to door, as a cleric i wasn't in range of his breath or whatever so my FR wasn't too important maybe. since i have like really crappy magic resistance as well my screen always said &quot;you lose control of yourself&quot; but i wouldn't be running. why is this? not in his line of sight? in fact, only times i've been feared to run were when i was summoned and that basically saved my life. are you actually supposed to resist the fears, poor me, i don't even know because i've never seen a resist message hehe. so ... i want to know, should i really try to boost my resistance? doesn't seem like its important for clerics. i donno.<br>
am i just being delusional? help.<br>
<br>
veraphie 52 vicar</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2F2F4F><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uanikacrystalwind.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Anika Crystalwind</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.pconcall.com/Images/eyes.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>10</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>2/27/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3:49:08 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.pconcall.com/Images/eaw.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: newbie ques about naggy</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Well, as far as fire resistance is concerned, in *most* cases, since heals aren't blocked by walls or obstacles, clerics will be placed safely out of the effect radius of the primary fear/AE spells that Naggy casts.  This means that you don't have to have the FR that a warrior or a nuking caster would have to have to survive those attacks (sine they are right in front of him), so usually you can get away without too much FR gear.  However, mistakes and bugs do happen, so it's never a bad idea to be prepared.  Not to mention the occasional summoning when you fire off a CH. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
As to the fear thing, I don't know - I've gotten a lot of situations where I'll get the message but don't actually move.  I consider it a blessing.  /shrug</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#212141><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/usllackblader.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sllack Blader</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://24.221.41.117:8080/images/adder65.jpg BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>59</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>2/27/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>8:06:31 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://24.221.41.117:8080/images/adder65.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: newbie ques about naggy</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Think outside the box. Screw the fire resist gear and jack up your magic res...<br>
<br>
As a cleric even if you do get hit from the AE fire, you will be buffed enough so you dont insta die and the AE fear which is a MUCH wider area cover will catch you and make you run back and forth letting your tanks die.<br>
<br>
100 total (with buffs) fire resist will be sufficient, get your magic up to 100 at least too so you resist some fears.<br>
</font><P>Bllack Ader - Dr00d in Agony. Arf!<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2F2F4F><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uroggelmustaffafez.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Roggel MustaffaFez</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://members.tripod.co.uk/redhotant/icons/iconoc03.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>32</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>2/28/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>2:20:13 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.austinpowers.com/EVIL/img/die_2.jpg border=0></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: newbie ques about naggy</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">get:<br>
